Banette (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0353: Shuppet
Pokémon
#0355: Duskull →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Banette (TCG Pocket).

Banette has been featured on 16 different cards since it debuted in the EX Hidden Legends expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Banette cards are normally Psychic-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Banette

Banette
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
